WEBVTT

11:07.584 --> 11:10.087
Can we go??

11:16.718 --> 11:19.805
I always wanted to!

11:19.888 --> 11:22.933
Since Kenji and I were little.

14:43.592 --> 14:44.467
She's nice.

14:44.551 --> 14:46.011
She's nuts!

14:46.094 --> 14:47.554
No, she's not.

14:47.637 --> 14:49.973
Let's get it over with!

14:50.056 --> 14:51.141
Fine.

44:29.125 --> 44:31.669
It was never about
the roller coaster.

44:37.592 --> 44:41.930
Kenji and I didn't have
a childhood.

44:47.602 --> 44:50.063
I just did the same thing

44:50.146 --> 44:53.024
to that little girl
and her brother.

44:54.275 --> 44:58.655
How can they ever
be children again?

45:07.664 --> 45:14.087
I'll never be a normal girl
who likes roller coasters.

45:15.755 --> 45:19.175
I'm broken
and can never be fixed.

45:20.885 --> 45:26.099
Because of this poison,
this curse in my veins.
